        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><h4 id="一，下载node-js"><a href="#一，下载node-js" class="headerlink" title="一，下载node.js"></a>一，<strong>下载node.js</strong></h4></blockquote><p>前往<a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/">node.js中文官网</a>下载，安装也很简单一直下一步就可以了。完成就绪，验证一下是否安装成功：按住<strong>win+R</strong>键打开运行框，输入<strong>cmd</strong>进入命令窗口，输入<strong>node -v</strong>回车，显示出版本号则是成功。<br><img "" class="lazyload" data-original="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210106212333789.png" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><blockquote><h4 id="二，安装Git"><a href="#二，安装Git" class="headerlink" title="二，安装Git"></a>二，<strong>安装Git</strong></h4></blockquote><ol><li><p><strong>下载</strong><br>前往<a href="https://git-scm.com/">Git官网下载</a>,由于网络环境因素，可能下载的非常慢，可以复制下载链接到迅雷下载。</p></li><li><p><strong>安装</strong><br>没有特殊需要的话一直Next就行了。<br>安装完成在桌面空白处单击右键，就会发现多了两个选项：<br><img "" class="lazyload" data-original="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210106213709127.png" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><p>点击<strong>Git Bash Here</strong>打开命令窗口，输入<strong>git –version</strong>，回车，如果出现版本号则说明安装成功。<br><img "" class="lazyload" data-original="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210106214245114.png" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><blockquote><h4 id="三，安装Hexo"><a href="#三，安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="三，安装Hexo"></a>三，<strong>安装Hexo</strong></h4></blockquote><p>前面的准备工作已经完成，下面就开始Hexo的安装。</p></li><li><p><strong>本地安装hexo</strong><br>首先在本地建立一个空文件夹，用来存放hexo文件和以后要写的博客文件，注意不要有中文。我在这里是在D盘建了一个MyBlog文件夹。<br>在新建的文件夹里单击右键，选择<strong>Git Bash Here</strong>，进入命令窗口依次输入以下命令：</p></li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 安装 hexo 框架</span><br><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 初始化文件夹</span><br><span class="line">hexo init</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 安装 hexo 依赖包</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这三条命令不是一下全输进去而是输一个回车一下。三条命令执行成功，Hexo 框架在本地就已经搭建好了。<br> 2. <strong>查看本地博客效果</strong><br>在<strong>Git Bash Here</strong>命令行窗口依次输入以下代码：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 生成静态网站</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"># 启动服务器</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时，打开浏览器，输入网址<a href="http://localhost:4000/%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC">http://localhost:4000/，就可以看到我们</a> Hexo 搭建的博客示例了。如下图（这是hexo默认主题）：<br><img "" class="lazyload" data-original="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210107112839496.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3oxOTA1Nzk2MjM0,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>]]></content>
      
      
